              },
              {
                "type": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "p",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Scope creep without clear runtime assumptions"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "p",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Service Contract"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "p",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Existing assets with predictable duty"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "p",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Slow escalation if SLAs are vague"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "tr",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "p",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Purchase"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "p",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Stable long-term load profile"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "td",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "p",
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Underestimating lifecycle support cost"
                      }
                    ]
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "props": {
          "align": []
        }
      },
      {
        "type": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Build acceptance criteria before contract award, not after mobilisation."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Require clear commissioning evidence and support contacts in writing."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Include operator capability and documentation quality in supplier scoring."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Review end-of-term options early to avoid expensive transition decisions."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Using the same matrix across projects makes procurement outcomes more consistent and easier to defend with finance, operations, and governance teams."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Standardise Commissioning And Handover To Protect Reliability"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Commissioning and handover quality often determines whether a project starts smoothly or carries hidden reliability debt. A standard handover pack should travel with every asset and include baseline settings, alarm status, maintenance intervals, and response pathways. Network-facing details should also be checked against local utility guidance from "
          },
          {
            "type": "a",
            "url": "https://www.energex.com.au/",
            "title": null,
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Energex"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " where relevant."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "ul",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Use one handover template across hire periods and owned assets."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Attach commissioning test evidence and unresolved defect actions."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Record emergency contacts and escalation windows in an operator-ready format."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "li",
            "children": [
              {
                "type": "lic",
                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Include logistics notes and access assumptions for transport teams via "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "a",
                    "url": "https://www.tmr.qld.gov.au/",
                    "title": null,
                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Transport and Main Roads"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "With consistent records, high-runtime generator fleets can reduce onboarding delays, shorten fault triage time, and preserve confidence during high-pressure operating windows."
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
